            "notes": "The deck focuses on utilizing Toph's abilities as an aggro commander to quickly ramp up mana production and overwhelm the opponent with a wide variety of creatures and direct damage spells. The key strategy is to efficiently ramp into powerful threats while disrupting the opponent's game plan with removal and combat tricks. By utilizing a mix of efficient mana dorks, land ramp spells, and direct damage spells, the deck aims to maintain a fast-paced and proactive playstyle. Additionally, the deck includes a selection of versatile creatures with abilities that provide additional value and resilience, ensuring that Toph can maintain pressure on the opponent while also protecting her own board state."
